{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-167-investigating-ulam-sequences","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 167: Istraživanje Ulam sekvence","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za pozitivne cele brojeve $a$ i $b$, Ulam niz $U(a,b)$ definisan je sa ${U{(a,b)}_1} = a$, ${U{(a,b)}_2} = b$, a za $k > 2$, ${U{(a,b)}_k}$ je najmanji ceo broj manji od ${U{(a,b)}_{(k-1)}}$ koji se može zapisati samo na jedan način kao zbir dva različita prethodna člana $U(a,b)$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, niz $U(1,2)$ počinje sa</p>\n<p>$$1, 2, 3 = 1 + 2, 4 = 1 + 3, 6 = 2 + 4, 8 = 2 + 6, 11 = 3 + 8$$</p>\n<p>5 nije unutar jer $5 = 1 + 4 = 2 + 3$ ima dve reprezentacije kao zbir dva početna člana, slično $7 = 1 + 6 = 3 + 4$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\sum {U(2, 2n + 1)_k}$ za $2 ≤ n ≤ 10$, gde je $k = {10}^{11}$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4141000cf542c50ff26","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301801,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-167-investigating-ulam-sequences"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function ulamSequences() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nulamSequences();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>ulamSequences()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>3916160068885</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(ulamSequences(), 3916160068885);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-167-investigating-ulam-sequences"